<br>
I can show you a number of reasons why NBG doesn't work. I can show you a number of reasons why FFA doesnt work. But both arguments depend upon people with no honour.<br>
<br>
Need before greed is abused daily by people who hide those weapons to roll on another. By tanks who intend to sell their new armour that just dropped. By casters rolling on items and spells they already have. The list goes on.<br>
<br>
